&lt;h1 id="google-should-pull-an-android-on-facebook"&gt;Google should pull an Android on Facebook&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jul 7 2011&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Android&amp;rsquo;s best weapon against iOS is that it&amp;rsquo;s a much more open platform. iOS&amp;rsquo; elegant user experience comes at a cost – developers have to suffer through approval delays, rejections, private APIs, rules against advertising, and shutdowns. Android, on the other hand is open to carriers, users, and developers.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>What I've Learned from Hacker News</title><link>https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_en/hackernews/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_en/hackernews/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_zh/hackernews/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
