&lt;h1 id="what-ive-learned-from-hacker-news"&gt;What I&amp;rsquo;ve Learned from Hacker News&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;February 2009&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hacker News was two years old last week. Initially it was supposed to be a side project—an application to sharpen Arc on, and a place for current and future Y Combinator founders to exchange news. It&amp;rsquo;s grown bigger and taken up more time than I expected, but I don&amp;rsquo;t regret that because I&amp;rsquo;ve learned so much from working on it.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>